nz.co.jedsimson.lgp.core.evolution.fitness

Class SingleOutputFitnessContext<TData>

  • FitnessContext
    • nz.co.jedsimson.lgp.core.evolution.fitness.SingleOutputFitnessContext<TData>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Module

    public class SingleOutputFitnessContext<TData>
extends FitnessContext

    Facilitates fitness evaluation for programs which have a single output.

    For programs with multiple outputs, class MultipleOutputFitnessContext should be used.

    See Also:
